 <td rowspan="5" width="223" valign="top">   Higher inland water temperatures 
  </td> <td width="360" valign="top">   Reduction in fish stocks 
  </td> <td width="300" valign="top">   Increased stratification and reduced mixing of water in lakes, reducing primary productivity and ultimately food supplies for fish species 
  </td> 
